# Assets Investment Total Excluding Derivatives Directly Held Amount

## identifier
de13145

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of total investments. Investments represent the purchase of a financial product or other item of value with an expectation of favourable future returns. This item excludes directly held derivatives.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.Investment.TotalExcludingDerivativesDirectlyHeld.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo7.02.14
- period=instant
